welcome: GoQba Medical provides automatic and objective services through AI-powered algorithms
products_text: It's an AI service that improves the process of manually creating assessments and and calculate a total score.
beery: (Name) is a solution that automatically scores Beery VMI-6 answer sheets with an AI model and provides results.
sperm: (Name) is a solution where an AI model analyzes sperm movement and gives a numerical rating.
hodu: Hodu is a rehabilitation monitoring and customized mild cognitive impairment rehabilitation content through cognitive testing.
contact_text: Complete the form below to connect with our team of experts on implementing digital primary care solutions.
partners_text: We're working on cross-business partnerships to better serve you.
success_signup_text: Press OK and you'll be taken to the homepage.
password_instruction: Password must have a Good or Strong rating. Password must be at least 8 characters long. Good password contain either a combination of uppercase and lowercase letters or a combination of letters and one digit. Strong passwords contain either a combination of letters and more than one digit or special characters.
setting_text: If you want to make any changes, just enter them and hit the Save button.
back_main: Press OK to go to the main.
login_first: You cannot use without log in.
beery_heading: AI-powered Beery VMI answer scoring tool
beery_text: Insert the patient's Beery VMI answer sheet to proceed with grading.
beery_file_rule: Beery VMI answer sheets should be one of these formats .pdf, .png .jpg .jpeg, etc.
beery_result_text: Select the patient number on the left to see the results for that number.
